sequenceDiagram
    participant Customer
    participant System
    participant Database
    participant Payment as Payment Gateway
    
    Customer->>System: 1. Browse
    System->>Database: 2. Get Tours
    Database->>System: 3. Return Tours
    System->>Customer: 4. Show Tours
    
    Customer->>System: 5. Select Tour
    System->>Database: 6. Check Availability
    Database->>System: 7. Availability
    System->>Customer: 8. Booking Form
    
    Customer->>System: 9. Submit Form
    System->>Database: 10. Create Booking
    Database->>System: 11. Booking Created
    System->>Customer: 12. Payment Page
    
    Customer->>System: 13. Submit Payment
    System->>Payment: 14. Process Payment
    Payment->>System: 15. Payment Result
    System->>Database: 16. Update Status
    Database->>System: 17. Status Updated
    System->>Customer: 18. Confirmation